{"tid":1295312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"捐錢 - 香港民意研究計劃 HKPOP","createTime":"2019-07-08T03:39:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:56:39.000Z","uid":24044,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26aebe411cf5c0b2d3038facef8c11b63262163c","tid":1295312,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"【延續追蹤民調 分析特首民望】<br />\n<br />\n追蹤民調是屬於香港人的溫度計，即使面對過風風雨雨，鍾庭耀博士堅持讓數字展示民意。我們將致力延續特首高官追蹤民調，以客觀、專業的態度分析香港民情。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所期望承繼以往的方式，每兩星期發放民調數字，預算研究經費為每月 24 萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n只要有 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2,400 位香港人登記成為普通會員並月捐 $100</span></strong>，就足以支持這項有 28 年歷史的民意調查。現誠邀大家共同參與：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/subscription\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fsubscription&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4VzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=e75c07f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/subscription</a><br />\n<br />\n#自己民調自己撐 #加入我們成為民研之友<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/65850708_478052019625898_698274627637477376_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_eui2=AeHr2y2v_lOka4e7ghJUp7iGwxaum24T5vzT2Gs66l4NamN7UEJLlJYuCr28g1En7llR_5ZgEjaKPISJ1zTN2vsZDX6b-lAn5-ocoMFM9K66aA&amp;_nc_oc=AQnE5q0mBQ42j0wXoyHlhFWJqi6w4lqu-sP3m_IPdlgNqp7Ph3RrpEzbNUYbM6ggeJY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=b0246d0909357d78d8000e7054704d85&amp;oe=5DB3C45C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F65850708_478052019625898_698274627637477376_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_eui2%3DAeHr2y2v_lOka4e7ghJUp7iGwxaum24T5vzT2Gs66l4NamN7UEJLlJYuCr28g1En7llR_5ZgEjaKPISJ1zTN2vsZDX6b-lAn5-ocoMFM9K66aA%26_nc_oc%3DAQnE5q0mBQ42j0wXoyHlhFWJqi6w4lqu-sP3m_IPdlgNqp7Ph3RrpEzbNUYbM6ggeJY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3Db0246d0909357d78d8000e7054704d85%26oe%3D5DB3C45C&h=cfc5e325&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"255ef1b2e9c2572f9fc57f9ac9d4205150ca1f77","tid":1295312,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:40:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190630/large/1561887837_5962.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190630%2Flarge%2F1561887837_5962.png&h=4ad5a0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港大民意研究計劃成立至今28年，是本地民意調查重要指標，由特首民望、政府表現以至港人身份認同，都是港人掌握社會風向的參考要素。<br />\n相關新聞：港大民研轉型惜捐款遠遜預期 鍾庭耀今重啟眾籌盼特首民調不斷纜<br />\n<br />\n民研計劃由7月1日起轉型為獨立機構「香港民意研究所」，依靠公民捐款維持運作，4月底曾宣佈要一次過籌募600萬元起動基金，惟爆出反惡法風波後，研究所主席鍾庭耀僅指「社會有其他事更需要資源」而主動停止募捐，是以至今僅籌得2萬元。<br />\n<strong>民研計劃現急需捐款資助，若在3、4日內未能籌得足夠經費，原來每兩星期發佈一次的特首民望調查，將於今個月內「斷纜」。</strong><br />\n相關新聞：嘆學術界變現實功利 鍾庭耀「安然」離開港大<br />\n<br />\n沒有客觀公正數據，事實或許從此淹沒在資訊洪流當中。要企硬、要力撐，我們就要全盤掌握動向，就要透徹了解真相。<br />\n捐款支持「香港民意研究所」： <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4VzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=59c6c8cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a> ，讓數據說實話，讓數據揭真相。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190708/59773000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59773000&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4VzbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=cd75b998\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190708%2F59773000&h=250c083c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190708/59773000</a>"},{"pid":"002ae13947cdabdd580cd92f169888409c14b232","tid":1295312,"uid":27194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:14:51.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318c026eef53719f2c86478951ecdefbbd4f679d","tid":1295312,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:29:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c768b5760a61177ea1e66a67ccee45cb3f4c54c","tid":1295312,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:23:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"353860df1a98f2eec2746ea15abf1a22c6d1f644","tid":1295312,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"503d37a01871a49061761d8e869f75f866773c39","tid":1295312,"uid":263943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"課左，推"},{"pid":"a5de530b0545fc7a1a037547ea23831a87a12cfb","tid":1295312,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:14:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb40398a86c533d057f5cf0d6a5c810992b33b9b","tid":1295312,"uid":35953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:18:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981a33325fe63de62426f7ccae927c892ed71147","tid":1295312,"uid":265544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"426672df43d25d76113f4c3e75c2132541d0530e","tid":1295312,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:56:39.000Z","msg":"推"}]}